Introduction

Jaehee is a South Korean singer under SM Entertainment. He is a member of NCT and its Japan-based sub-unit NCT Wish.

He was first introduced as a participant in the survival show NCT Universe: LASTART. He was introduced in Episode 4. He ranked 3rd in the show, earning his spot in the Japanese unit.
